genresAdvancedInfo.name: arunachal indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Arunachal indie is a genre of music that originated in the Indian state of Arunachal Pradesh. It is a fusion of traditional folk music and contemporary western music. Arunachal indie is characterized by its use of indigenous instruments and rhythms, as well as its incorporation of modern production techniques. The genre is gaining popularity in India and beyond, as more artists explore the unique sounds and rhythms of Arunachal Pradesh.
